Human is an Uncomplicated Model of Anatomy


You are here to evaluate HUMAn, a physiological model that is used to simulate the evolution of patients with different traumas

You have not finished all the cases.

Please use the menu on the left to complete your reviews.

Well done!

You have completed all the cases!

You still have opportunity to check your answers using the left menu.

Once you are satisfied, please validate your results using the button below.
